{
  "stem": "5496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I perfected it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But somehow, we manage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I just want to say that the Italians were the most lovely, the most warm-hearted, compassionate, and delightful people you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were kind and nice, and they really closed an eye.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They knew we are there illegally, yet they never made any distinction between food stamps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I believe they still had-- this is, after all, right after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Milano, and from there we went to Rome.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That I remember, by train-- now, how she managed to get train tickets, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because during all this time, our total possession were three single dollar bills.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was between my aunt and I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How she got them, she must have sold-- she had some things with her-- a camera, something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She must have sold some of her stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got to Rome , because where her son was, and that's the only family that we knew was in Rome.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we landed, indeed, in Rome.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With her son?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I suppose, very warm and very great, and the Italian family were extremely nice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed with them a very short time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after that, we were sort of made-- feel a bit uncomfortable, on their part.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I must add, not to the Italian, the real Italian people, who was a lovely grandmother and her son, to whom this aunt was married to.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was a high-ranking officer in the Naval ministry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were as nice as can be.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But somehow, the two aunts, they objected that we stay there that length of time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one of them, my aunt then-- later on in years-- told me that she complained that I took two pieces of bread in the morning.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
